  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Cost effectiveness between PPCI and thrombolytic therapy in STEMI patients without
      contraindications
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Cost effectiveness between PPCI and thrombolytic therapy in STEMI patients 100 patient each
      within 90 m for PPCI and 6h for thrombolytic
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
